{
  "page": "Godswood of Highgarden",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>godswood of Highgarden</b> is found at <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>, the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. It contains three <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwoods</a> known as the <b>Three Singers</b>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Godswood_of_Highgarden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>'s renowned <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood\" title=\"Godswood\">godswood</a> is lush and green. Instead of having a single <a href=\"/index.php/Heart_tree\" title=\"Heart tree\">heart tree</a> like most godswoods, Highgarden's wood contains three towering and graceful <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwoods</a>. The limbs of the ancient weirwoods have grown so entangled over time that they look like one single tree, albeit with three trunks. Located beneath the so-called Three Singers is a tranquil pool.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Godswood_of_Highgarden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Three Singers are said to have been planted by <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_Greenhand\" title=\"Garth Greenhand\">Garth Greenhand</a> in antiquity.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Although <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_IX_Gardener\" title=\"Garth IX Gardener\">Garth IX Gardener</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a>, built the first <a href=\"/index.php/Sept\" title=\"Sept\">sept</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>, he continued to pray within the castle's <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood\" title=\"Godswood\">godswood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Godswood_of_Highgarden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_highgarden.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Reach: Highgarden.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_andals_in_the_reach.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Reach: Andals in the Reach.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404195019\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 259/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8616/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 948/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 414/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    9.279      1 -total\n 76.81%    7.127      3 Template:Ref\n 43.67%    4.052      3 Template:Ref/core\n 20.79%    1.929      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:23448-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404195019 and revision id 329573\n -->\n",
